{"tid":1886813,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA 打造限量版《電馭叛客 2077》主題 GeForce RTX 2080 Ti　將送出限量 77 張","createTime":"2020-02-19T07:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T11:39:32.000Z","uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4dda4bb3e2f96959f254afa4cbd1d24655a7d307","tid":1886813,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA 宣布打造限量版規格《電馭叛客 2077》主題 GeForce RTX 2080 Ti，並將透過活動送出限量 77 張。<br />\n <br />\n  由波蘭遊戲開發暨發行商 CD Projekt RED 打造的《電馭叛客 2077》是款第一人稱科幻角色扮演遊戲，故事以 2077 年的美國虛構巨大都會「夜城（NightCry）」為舞台，敘述國家失去公權力，充斥著透過改造肉體將發揮極限潛能的生化人，並衍生出許多問題。玩家將以傭兵身分來體驗這個混亂的世界。<br />\n <br />\n  今日官方宣布推出以《電馭叛客 2077》為主題的限量 NVIDIA GPU。NVIDIA 表示：「此款《電馭叛客 2077》限量版規格 GeForce RTX 2080 Ti 與 GeForce RTX 2080 Ti 創始版本相同，而該 GPU 是基於 NVIDIA 與 CD PROJEKT RED 緊密的合作關係所共同打造，以表達 NVIDIA 對《電馭叛客 2077》的期待與熱愛。《電馭叛客 2077》將於今年推出，預計將帶來一個令人驚豔的光線追蹤世界。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/66/827a5768acbe5e0e84d9971cd317s4q5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F66%2F827a5768acbe5e0e84d9971cd317s4q5.JPG&h=5dcd966e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/65/624bb64994b6457f7a5c9ed1b817s4p5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F65%2F624bb64994b6457f7a5c9ed1b817s4p5.JPG&h=ba2a4668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/34/820a2173cd35a78b7c0768de7517s9e5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F34%2F820a2173cd35a78b7c0768de7517s9e5.JPG&h=a7fcd4c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_KK3fBWxnEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_KK3fBWxnEo&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=4cffa7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_KK3fBWxnEo</a><br />\n量《電馭叛客 2077》GPU 將透過活動方式送出，官方指出參加 #RTXOn 贈獎活動就有機會贏得此款不超過 200 個的 GPU，成為限量 77 名的幸運兒之一；活動於即日起至 2020 年 2 月 28 日止，詳細參加辦法可至官方頁查詢。<br />\n <br />\n  《電馭叛客 2077》預定 2020 年 9 月 17 日問世。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=192859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D192859&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=5d46303b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=192859</a>"},{"pid":"1a3b20b48d3840dddc6027ae33de89c7259bcb64","tid":1886813,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"無香港份"},{"pid":"b397f72e1fc2348691b2b6b7f8c87ac69c0473dc","tid":1886813,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"冇驚玩，整幾耐都冇用"},{"pid":"71b1f35ea5ad4385ad8a12ab6ad20190c120c53a","tid":1886813,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWX2m1d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWX2m1d.gif&h=f26d93c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oN1VG1e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoN1VG1e.gif&h=63ee98cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewbq4ey.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fewbq4ey.gif&h=cca3bdbe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"179a26260e5937571c4aac84d69af6a